"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1928594-Coco-Gauff-Olympic-Games-tennis\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Coco Gauff will finally get the chance to become an Olympian this summer, with the WTA Tour star a part of the United States team that has headed to Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Coco Gauff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\"}, {\"begin\": 54, \"end\": 62, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999913284214834, \"rank\": 8.671518238017882e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 113, \"end\": 126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998151964350842, \"rank\": 0.00014951425956405385, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 151, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999757826575, \"rank\": 2.4217347034739577e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games are already underway, with the Opening Ceremony taking place on the Seine River on Friday evening, withGauffthe flag bearer.\", \"from\": 158, \"to\": 292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 199, \"end\": 215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9988871986112356, \"rank\": 0.0010549578995108686, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tennis event kicks off on Saturday, and the 20-year-old is included in the draw.\", \"from\": 294, \"to\": 378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It will be the first time the American will play under the Olympic rings for her country, having been forced to miss the previous edition in Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 542, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 409, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999997336366187, \"rank\": 1.6551408024778613e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 520, \"end\": 525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9883421170414866, \"rank\": 0.011794473706681127, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the 2021 Olympics taking place in the midst of theCOVID-19 pandemic, Gauff was one of the unfortunate athletes who lost out on their dream after contracting the virus in the build-up.\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has always been a dream of mine to represent the USA at the Olympics,\\\" she said in a statement at the time.\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 844, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope there will be many more chances for me to make this come true in the future.\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 930, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to wish TEAM USA the best of luck and safe games for every Olympian and the entire Olympic family.\\\"\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 1037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 946, \"end\": 954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.5553219812020032, \"rank\": 0.6005806807666733, \"text\": \"TEAM USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 997, \"end\": 1005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999913284214834, \"rank\": 8.671518238017882e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fortunately for Gauff, that opportunity has come back around, with the added honor of carrying the U.S. flag at the opening ceremony alongsideLeBron James.\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1140, \"end\": 1149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999988413037, \"rank\": 1.1588004609685952e-09, \"text\": \"U.S. flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wanted to cry when I found out but my whole team was there, so I went in the corner and I did it,\\\" Gauff said of being selected.\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I truly am in shock and I do not take it for granted I am going to try to take it all in and I know this will be a memory I will remember for the rest of my life.\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Honestly, walking around the village last night, so many people came up and congratulated me.\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1586, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1807, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Opening Ceremony Flag Bearer@CocoGauff.The moment Coco got the news from her teammate@chris_eubanks96\\u2026#ParisOlympicspic.twitter.com/yjIWPjm6J1  \\\"Even some of the people who were on Team USA who I guess voted for me who I did not know.\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 2066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2013, \"end\": 2021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.5553219812020032, \"rank\": 0.6005806807666733, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were like, 'Yeah, I was one of the people who nominated you and we could not ask for a better person.'\\\"\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gauff's Olympics starts Saturday in the doubles alongside Jessica Pegula against Ellen Perez and Darian Saville of Australia.\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2235, \"end\": 2249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Pegula\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jessica Pegula\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Pegula\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Pegula\"}, {\"begin\": 2258, \"end\": 2269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellen_Perez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ellen Perez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellen_Perez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellen_Perez\"}, {\"begin\": 2281, \"end\": 2288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Saville\", \"score\": 0.9913355061944783, \"rank\": 0.00873990709025839, \"text\": \"Saville\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Saville\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Saville\"}, {\"begin\": 2292, \"end\": 2301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.5696007949328958, \"rank\": 0.5017234438346672, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She will then do battle with the Australians in the singles a day later against Ajla Tomljanovic.\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2383, \"end\": 2399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ajla_Tomljanovi\\u0107\", \"score\": 0.9999999996557563, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ajla Tomljanovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ajla_Tomljanovi\\u0107\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ajla_Tomljanovi\\u0107\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2571, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2539, \"end\": 2552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.7506492936746414e-13, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2588, \"end\": 2601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\":